headline: Mitsubishi Electric Trane HVAC US Names Tim Vordenbaumen Chief Financial Officer
summary: SUWANEE, Ga., August 27, 2025--METUS welcomes Tim Vordenbaumen, CPA, as the company’s new Chief Financial Officer.
